Updated: 10/4/2012

A collection of utilities and libraries that corresponds with the "Building a Better Emulator" series on http://thecobraden.blogspot.com.

This contains:
framework.jar 		A modified "/system/framework/framework.jar" for API 10 that allows control over TelephonyManager values
device_ids.txt		A sample device ID file.  This should be placed in "/mnt/sdcard/"
DeviceIDChanger/	An application Eclipse project and APK for making changes to the "device_ids.txt" file

-jakev
